summary:
Experienced Geoscientist with a history of working in the oil & gas industry. Skilled in Reservoir Geology, Exploration Geology, Seismic Interpretation, Static Modelling, Reservoir Management and Operations. Now working as an all-rounder in Geothermal Energy.
Strong research professional with a Master of Science (MSc) in International Management from the University of Liverpool and Geology from the University of Utrecht.
